<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-7">
        <p>My Name is Anthony Conrad, and I am an aspiring Ruby on Rails web developer (I'm on the right).</p>

        <p>I am currently attending Purdue University as a computer science student, while attempting to become a Junior Web Developer. I beileve that Ruby on Rails is one of the best frameworks for web develeopment and I enjoy creating applications with clear and concise code. </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#skill"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="skill"
          >
            Skills
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="skill">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>